Eskom’s Koeberg Nuclear Plant Unit Resumes Power Generation After Failure

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-09-08T09:04:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/eskom-s-koeberg-nuclear-plant-unit-resumes-power-generation-after-failure.html
Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. said its
Koeberg nuclear power plant’s Number 2 unit in  South Africa 
returned to service after an unplanned shutdown on Sept. 5.  The unit, one of only two at the plant, is “back on full
load since the early hours of this morning,” Eskom spokeswoman
Hilary Joffe said in a mobile phone text message today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  